name: TIME TO CHANGE
description:
it’s all started in that night 
Everything’s the same
THE darkness and routine never ends
SO, it’s time to change 

the cat starts his journey and 
been through lots of problems 
Maybe there’s no way but he keep on going 
AND finally find something 
don’t know exactly this is what he wants,
just feel it, So he stay

AND the Sun finally raised
it’s a hope , goal or maybe it’s temporary 
It doesn’t matter anymore, better enjoy the moment 
Cause we never know when see the sun again
